BATTLE CRY				CATEGORY:Feat	TYPE:General.Skill	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=7		PREVARGTEQ:Modifier_Intimidation,3			PRETEXT:Prerequisites master in Intimidation										DESC:When you roll initiative, you can yell a mighty battle cry and Demoralize an observed foe as a free action. If you're legendary in Intimidation, you can use a reaction to Demoralize your foe when you critically succeed at an attack roll.

BATTLE MEDICINE			CATEGORY:Feat	TYPE:General.Healing.Manipulate.Skill	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=1		PREVARGTEQ:Modifier_Medicine,1			PRETEXT:Prerequisites trained in Medicine											DESC:You can patch up yourself or an adjacent ally, even in combat. Attempt a Medicine check with the same DC as for Treat Wounds and provide the corresponding amount of healing. As with Treat Wounds, you can attempt checks against higher DCs if you have the minimum proficiency rank. The target is then temporarily immune to your Battle Medicine for 1 day.

