TITAN WRESTLER				CATEGORY:Feat	TYPE:General.Skill	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=1		PREVARGTEQ:Modifier_Athletics,1			PRETEXT:Prerequisites trained in Athletics											DESC:You can attempt to Disarm, Grapple, Shove, or Trip creatures up to two sizes larger than you, or up to three sizes larger than you if you're legendary in Athletics.

